definitions.definition: To make a rustling sound while moving.
To flourish with a swishing sound.
examples: to swish a cane back and forth

definitions.definition: To make a successful basketball shot that does not touch the rim or backboard .
To mince or otherwise to behave in an effeminate manner.
examples: I shall not swish ; I'll merely act limp-wristed.

definitions.definition: To cause a liquid to move around in a container, or in one's mouth.
examples: Swish the mouthwash around the mouth and between the teeth for one minute.

main_definition: To make a rustling sound while moving.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive ) To flourish with a swishing sound.
( transitive , slang , dated ) To flog ; to lash .
( basketball ) To make a successful basketball shot that does not touch the rim or backboard .
( gay slang ) To mince or otherwise to behave in an effeminate manner.
( transitive ) To cause a liquid to move around in a container, or in one's mouth.
